<task id="task_2D52E2DB4C1E4F319564B7C937769258">
  <title>Deactivate a Campaign</title>
  <shortdesc>Deactivate a campaign to shut it down. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <context id="context_53C9CABB2B7B4A34BCB2E43240D49140">
      <p>When you deactivate a campaign, it is stopped immediately. No visitors
		  will see the campaign's content. Its status changes to Unapproved. 
		</p>
    </context>
    <steps id="steps_F6DDFC39AE4F4BB8BDB6F2C783E33A83">
      <step id="step_8F39C5C2F75F4AEF9EE70D2653F5B2E6">
        <cmd>Click 
			 <uicontrol>deactivate</uicontrol> to shut down a campaign
			 immediately. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>When you deactivate a campaign, you are asked if you want to move
				the campaign to the library. Choose 
				<uicontrol>yes</uicontrol> to move it to library. Choose 
				<uicontrol>no</uicontrol> to leave the campaign listed on the
				Campaigns Home Page. 
			 </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
